commit.message: Bump development status trove classifier: Beta -> Stable

Remove docstring of `batched` backport

Otherwise it shows up in the API reference.
Skip device not connected test if device is connected

Harmonize copyright notices

At the time of writing, the repository contains two copyright notices:

1. In the LICENSE file
2. In mkdocs.yaml

The MIT license template copyright notice has the following format:

Copyright <YEAR> <COPYRIGHT HOLDER>

Some sources suggest using a single year (the year of first publication),
whereas others suggest specifying every year in which a release was made. For
simplicity, I choose the former option.
Handle optional dependencies in pyproject.toml instead of tox.ini

For consistency with argparse builtins
